comingle.android.directory.ui.dialogsequences

Class AlertDialogSequence<D extends java.io.Serializable>

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Thread
      • comingle.android.directory.ui.dialogsequences.AlertDialogSequence<D>
  • Type Parameters:
    D - Type of administrative data handled by the directory.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Runnable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    DirectoryChoiceDialogSequence, LanSetupDialogSequence, WifiDirectSetupDialogSequence

    public class AlertDialogSequence<D extends java.io.Serializable>
extends java.lang.Thread
    This abstract class defines daemon thread routines that maintain a sequence of dialog boxes (created by DirectoryDialogBuilder) that prompts user for input parameters that customizes an instance of a BaseDirectory.
    Author:
    Edmund S.L. Lam
